videos.headline: Francois slings 17-yard TD pass for FSU
videos.description: Deondre Francois throws a 17-yard strike to Keith Gavin for an opening touchdown.

videos.headline: Miami finds the end zone on 4th down to tie the game.
videos.description: Miami's Lawrence Cager snags a slant on fourth down for 10-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Florida State brings out Turnover Backpack
videos.description: Florida State swats the ball from N'Kosi Perry and falls on it to set up great field position.

videos.headline: Terry grabs 17-yard pass from Francois for TD
videos.description: Tamorrion Terry hauls in a 17-yard pass from Deondre Francois to push Florida State's lead over Miami to 17-7.

videos.headline: Another scuffle breaks out between FSU & Miami
videos.description: Miami players run over to the Florida State sideline after a rough facemask penalty incites a confrontation between the two teams.

videos.headline: FSU's Matthews takes punt return 74 yards to the house
videos.description: D.J. Matthews breaks the game open for Florida State with a 74-yard punt return touchdown.

videos.headline: Miami's turnover chain makes an appearance with sack fumble
videos.description: Miami's defense comes up big forcing a fumble deep in FSU territory, which leads to a touchdown.

videos.headline: Cager catches fade to cut into FSU's lead
videos.description: Miami's Lawrence Cager leaps and brings down a touchdown pass to trim Florida State's lead to 27-14.

videos.headline: Miami's Pinckney intercepts FSU's Francois
videos.description: Deondre Francois throws a pick to Michael Pinckney to set up another Miami touchdown.

videos.headline: Miami's Perry lofts 17-yard TD pass
videos.description: Jeff Thomas turns and grabs 17-yard pass from N'Kosi Perry to cut FSU's lead to six.

videos.headline: Perry's 4th TD pass puts Miami ahead
videos.description: N'Kosi Perry brings Miami back throwing his fourth touchdown to Brevin Jordan to give the Hurricanes their first lead.
